ْبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaAbiyHu","text_ar":"مَصَابِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) —"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaAbiyHu Aln~ujuwmi","text_ar":"مَصَابِيحُ النُّجُومِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmu AlkawaAkibi","text_ar":"اَعْلَامُ الكَوَاكِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterisms, that are signs of the way to travellers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L, TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drinking-vessel of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaH","text_ar":"قَدَح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AHn, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSobaHN","text_ar":"مِصْبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaAbiyHu","text_ar":"مَصَابِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the pl. of the former] signifies the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vessels called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqodaAH","text_ar":"اَقْدَاح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaH","text_ar":"قَدَح"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one drinks the morning-draught called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabuwH","text_ar":"صَبُوح"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  And A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that remains in the morning in the place where she has lain down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not going forth to pasture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until the sun has risen high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of her strength"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and her fatness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the quality thus described is approved: (As, S, TA:) and such a she-camel is also termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSobaHN","text_ar":"مِصْبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl. of the former as above. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wide spear-head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such as are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asin~apN SubaAHiy~apN","text_ar":"اَسِنَّةٌ صُبَاحِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSobaHN","text_ar":"مِصْبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","L","Bd","Jel","TA","As"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}